title: Google\Cloud\BigQuery\DataTransfer\V1\StartManualTransferRunsRequest\TimeRange
name: TimeRange
description:
A specification for a time range, this will request transfer runs with run_time between start_time (inclusive) and end_time (exclusive).

Generated from protobuf message google.cloud.bigquery.datatransfer.v1.StartManualTransferRunsRequest.TimeRange

Extends Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message

params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.start_time
params.description: Start time of the range of transfer runs. For example, "2017-05-25T00:00:00+00:00". The start_time must be strictly less than the end_time. Creates transfer runs where run_time is in the range between start_time (inclusive) and end_time (exclusive).

params.name: data.end_time
params.description: End time of the range of transfer runs. For example, "2017-05-30T00:00:00+00:00". The end_time must not be in the future. Creates transfer runs where run_time is in the range between start_time (inclusive) and end_time (exclusive).
